---
layout: page2
title: "Ted Benson"
lozenge: blog
---

<div class="blog-list">

<p>This is a partial archive.. I'm porting back-posts over to the new site whenever I have a free minute..</p>

<div class="related">
  <table>
    {% for post in site.posts %}
    <tr>
      <td class="thumbcell">
       {% if post.thumbnail %}
       <a href="{{post.url}}"><img class="post-thumb" src="/images/blog/thumbnails/{{ post.thumbnail }}" /></a>
       {% endif %}
      </td>
      <td>
        <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.title }}</a><br />
        {% if post.tags %}
        <p class="tags">
        {% for tag in post.tags %}
        <span class="tag">{{tag}}</span>
        {% endfor %}
        </p>
        {% endif %}
        <span>{{ post.date | date: "%B %e, %Y" }}</span>
      </td>
    </tr>
  {% endfor %}
  </table>
  </div>
</div>

